channel.title: I am the biggest noob ever, help!
channel.description:
I just joined moparscape and this site :). Everything was running smooth until i couldn't get any npc with triple digits, when ever i try to get any npc like the kalphite queen it disconnects me :confused: please help. Also how do i get the admin crown and ancients?
One more problem, i have no idea how to join a server :P. Like how do i enter the password, how do i get in a specific server room, etc.
PLEASE HELP!

and TzTok-Jad is ::npc 2745, just like that. (No commma)

item.title: I am the biggest noob ever, help!
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Well, if the server itself has a password, then it’s a Hamachi server, and biggest noobs ever + hamachi servers do not mix. Otherwise, you get in a specific server room by clicking on the ground, and you don’t try to spawn things with more than 3 digits because the client is programmed rather poorly and will crash when it doesn’t know what else to do.
